# Containers with Middleware — local-dev/certs gitignore
#
# This directory contains generate-certs.sh (committed) and the files it generates (not committed).
# All generated certificate artefacts are excluded here and in local-dev/.gitignore.
#
# Never add real certificates, private keys, or keystores to Git.

# Private keys — owner-read only (chmod 600)
*.key

# Certificates
*.crt

# Combined PEM bundles (may contain private key material)
*.pem

# Keystores and truststores
*.p12
*.jks

# OpenSSL working files cleaned up by the script — excluded as belt-and-suspenders
*.csr
*.srl
*.cnf
